  <hr class="my-4">
   <p class="lead"> Connecting your seviipay account to Zapier will give your Zapier account access to a stream of orders placed by your customers that you can then connect to other services integrated with Zapier. </p>
  <hr class="my-4">
  <p class="lead">Each event sent to Zapier includes the entire schema for the order so you can filter different inovices to different actions in your Zap. </p>
